title: American Chopper: Senior vs. Junior - Mikey's Art Opening aired
description:
With commercials, crappy analog cable quality - take it or leave it. Don't know "S-E" data. This is the first new episode after the hiatus, air date: 25 April 2011.

PJD begins to build a bike for Jared Allen, while Junior meets with his lawyers over Senior's newest lawsuit; the OCC continues working on the custom project for Supernatural Cymbals; on opening night for his art gallery, Mikey is in the spotlight.
